column5: Planning another trip to the whities territory tomorrow.... The original plan changed a bit as my Bud is busy...sooooo...if anyone wants to come along PM me as soon as you can as I am trying to find a company.  Bright and early start ...  Cheers, Ice Fisherman
Boy, that sounds GREAT...however I am grounded for at least another 3-5 weeks.....my mouth drools every time I see them Whitefish on the ice.  GOOD LUCK TOMORROW  Bob

My buddy and I are heading out of oro tomorrow but probably won't be hitting the lake til about 9:30 or maybe a bit later.  Unfortunately it is only a two-man hut so no room to all fish together.  Feel free to pop by and say hi if you see us though.  I will be the one in the green snowboarding gear (plaid type pants) and blue plaid/fur hat dragging my clam 5600 on a homemade ski rig.   -Alphaalpha (Adam).

We'll be going out of Willow...no worry as we never use portable...planning to drive with the kids as we did last week...may meet you somewhere on the big lake   should be on the ice by about 8-8:30am :  Cheers, Ice Fisherman
